        "heading": "Where and how can you watch Crafter’s TV?",
        "text": "<p>Part of the Crafter’s Companion family, Crafter’s TV is a digital channel for all crafters, from total beginners to expert makers.<br\/><br\/>With more than 35 hours of live shows each week, you can tune in to a packed schedule of shows for all crafters, from total beginners to expert makers.<br\/><br\/>Join our friendly family of experts and presenters every day for new and exciting crafting products, live tutorials and inspiring demonstrations. This is a channel for all craft fans to discover our newest crafting innovations, learn a new technique and make new friends!<br\/><br\/>You can watch live via or catch up via our website, Facebook page or Youtube Channel.<br\/>Tune in using your phone, computer or even by streaming straight onto your TV.<br\/><br\/>So, wherever you are, it couldn't be simpler to tune in on yourfavourite devices and join the fun! Here's how...<\/p>"
